SQL_STMT_U.val: select isn, long_name , substring(long_comment, charindex('dStartDate', long_comment)+12,10) from eo where eo_type = 2280 and long_name like ':1' and isn in (select eo2_isn from relations where relation_type = 2712 and eo1_isn = :2) order by substring(long_comment, charindex('dStartDate', long_comment)+12,10)

Text.val: eoIsn can be either from the location city/region or from the entity id

ExpSyntax.val: 'Number of tickets purchased from "refer a friend" sender, to have free ticket'
'End time must be greater than start time'
'End date must be greater than start date'
